seeing the, my name on the sign of this building
and smelling the sewage in the cold North

00:38:00.569 --> 00:38:04.210
Dakota air and hearing "powp, powp, powp,
powp, powp, powp", which is the sound of people

00:38:04.210 --> 00:38:05.210
applauding in mittens.

00:38:05.210 --> 00:38:10.029
[audience laughs]

00:38:10.029 --> 00:38:12.509
That was my North Dakota experience.

