00:38:47.710 --> 00:38:49.079
[audience laughs]

00:38:49.079 --> 00:38:53.900
So, so, but I, I, I do it kind of all at the
end. It actually takes me almost two weeks

00:38:53.900 --> 00:38:59.109
of pretty much non-stop, but I get a, I get
a printout of all the, I do a lot of Googling

00:38:59.109 --> 00:39:03.789
during this phase of my year and get a, a,
get a, all the headlines for the year and

00:39:03.789 --> 00:39:07.799
then I start trying to come up with jokes
