&gt;&gt;Dave: The whole book thing, I mean--

00:40:13.769 --> 00:40:14.769
&gt;&gt;Older Male: Yes, he is.

00:40:14.769 --> 00:40:15.780
&gt;&gt;Dave: I'd just give it to him and say, "Read
